{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/convert-json-data-to-html","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"json-apis-and-ajax","demoType":null,"title":"Prevedi podatke iz JSON-a u HTML","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada počnete da dobijate podatke od API iz JSON, možete ga prikazati u HTML.</p>\n<p>Možete koristiti metodu <code>forEach</code> za pregled podataka jer su stavke slika mačaka sačuvane u nizu podataka. Kada dođete do svakog elementa, možete promeniti atribute HTML.</p>\n<p>Prvo, deklariši atribut HTML-a sa <code>let html = \"\";</code>.</p>\n<p>Zatim, iteriraj JSON, dodajući HTML u parametar koji prolazi kroz imena ključeva u oznakama <code>strong</code>, praćen vrednošću. Kada završiš iteraciju, prikaži.</p>\n<p>Ovo je kod koji radi ovo:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let html = '';\r\njson.forEach(function (val) {\r\n  const keys = Object.keys(val);\r\n  html += \"&#x3C;div class = 'cat'>\";\r\n  keys.forEach(function (key) {\r\n    html += '&#x3C;strong>' + key + '&#x3C;/strong>: ' + val[key] + '&#x3C;br>';\r\n  });\r\n  html += '&#x3C;/div>&#x3C;br>';\r\n});\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Za ovaj zadatak, morate dodati nove komponente za HTML na stranici, pa ne možete se oslonjati na <code>textContent</code>. Umesto toga, morate koristiti <code>innerHTML</code>, što može učiniti sajt ranjivim na napade cross-site scriptinga.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d7fae367417b2b2512be5","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Uspostujte način za <code>forEach</code> okruživanja podataka JSON i kreiranje komponenti HTML za prikazivanje.</p>\n<p>Ovo je primer za JSON:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-json\">[\r\n  {\r\n    \"id\": 0,\r\n    \"imageLink\": \"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/legacy-json-apis-ajax/funny-cat.jpg\",\r\n    \"altText\": \"A white cat wearing a green helmet shaped melon on its head. \",\r\n    \"codeNames\": [\"Juggernaut\", \"Mrs. Wallace\", \"Buttercup\"]\r\n  }\r\n]\n</code></pre>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"data-visualization","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":16807,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/convert-json-data-to-html"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\r\n    document.getElementById('getMessage').onclick = function () {\r\n      const req = new XMLHttpRequest();\r\n      req.open('GET', '/json/cats.json', true);\r\n      req.send();\r\n      req.onload = function () {\r\n        const json = JSON.parse(req.responseText);\r\n        let html = '';\r\n        // Add your code below this line\r\n\r\n        // Add your code above this line\r\n        document.getElementsByClassName('message')[0].innerHTML = html;\r\n      };\r\n    };\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  body {\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;\r\n  }\r\n  h1 {\r\n    font-size: 2em;\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n  }\r\n  .box {\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    background-color: #eee;\r\n    padding: 20px 5px;\r\n  }\r\n  button {\r\n    color: white;\r\n    background-color: #4791d0;\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    border: 1px solid #4791d0;\r\n    padding: 5px 10px 8px 10px;\r\n  }\r\n  button:hover {\r\n    background-color: #0f5897;\r\n    border: 1px solid #0f5897;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<h1>Cat Photo Finder</h1>\r\n<p class=\"message box\">The message will go here</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  <button id=\"getMessage\">Get Message</button>\r\n</p>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš kod treba da sačuva podatke u parametru <code>html</code></p>","testString":"assert.match(__helpers.removeWhiteSpace(code), /html(\\+=|=html\\+)/g);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod bi trebalo da koristi metodu <code>forEach</code> za obavotavanje podataka <code>JSON</code> iz <code>API</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /json\\.forEach/g);"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod treba da okruži imena polja u oznakama <code>strong</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code, /<strong>.+<\\/strong>/g);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/data-visualization/#json-apis-and-ajax","dashedName":"convert-json-data-to-html","certification":"data-visualization","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"data-visualization","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"json-apis-and-ajax","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/render-images-from-data-sources","prevChallengePath":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/access-the-json-data-from-an-api","id":"587d7fae367417b2b2512be5","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":6,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<script>\r\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {\r\n    document.getElementById('sendMessage').onclick = function () {\r\n      const userName = document.getElementById('name').value;\r\n      const url = 'https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts';\r\n      // Add your code below this line\r\n      const xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();\r\n      xhr.open('POST', url, true);\r\n      xhr.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json; charset=UTF-8');\r\n      xhr.onreadystatechange = function () {\r\n        if (xhr.readyState === 4 && xhr.status === 201) {\r\n          const serverResponse = JSON.parse(xhr.response);\r\n          document.getElementsByClassName('message')[0].textContent =\r\n            serverResponse.userName + serverResponse.suffix;\r\n        }\r\n      };\r\n      const body = JSON.stringify({\r\n        userName: userName,\r\n        suffix: ' loves cats!'\r\n      });\r\n      xhr.send(body);\r\n      // Add your code above this line\r\n    };\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<style>\r\n  body {\r\n    text-align: center;\r\n    font-family: 'Helvetica', sans-serif;\r\n  }\r\n  h1 {\r\n    font-size: 2em;\r\n    font-weight: bold;\r\n  }\r\n  .box {\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    background-color: #eee;\r\n    padding: 20px 5px;\r\n  }\r\n  button {\r\n    color: white;\r\n    background-color: #4791d0;\r\n    border-radius: 5px;\r\n    border: 1px solid #4791d0;\r\n    padding: 5px 10px 8px 10px;\r\n  }\r\n  button:hover {\r\n    background-color: #0f5897;\r\n    border: 1px solid #0f5897;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<h1>Cat Friends</h1>\r\n<p class=\"message\">Reply from Server will be here</p>\r\n<p>\r\n  <label for=\"name\"\r\n    >Your name:\r\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" />\r\n  </label>\r\n  <button id=\"sendMessage\">Send Message</button>\r\n</p>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/data-visualization/json-apis-and-ajax/convert-json-data-to-html"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}